<title>USA: Collins &amp; Aikman continues shr buyback.</title>
<headline>Collins &amp; Aikman continues shr buyback.</headline>
<dateline>CHARLOTTE, N.C. 1997-03-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>Collins &amp; Aikman Corp said on Friday that its board has approved a continuation of its stock repurchase program.</p>
<p>Collins &amp; Aikman said that it increased the amount of authorized expenditures for common share repurchases to $12 million from $10 million during fiscal 1997, the company said.</p>
<p>Collins &amp; Aikman has approximately 70 million shares outstanding.</p>
